block.kittytalents.cat_bed.set_owner_hel: Shift click with your cat nearby and they will come and make the bed their own. If the unimaginable happens and they do die right click the bed to revive them.
item.kittytalents.owner_change.tooltip: Sets ANY cat to be yours

treat.dire_treat.too_young: This cat's a bit too young to be learning skills just yet.

talent.kittytalents.bed_finder.descripti: While a cat with this skill is on your head, your bed will be highlighted in a black outline. To get the cat on you head, right click on them with a bone in hand. The range at which it can do this is equal to 200 blocks per level, but becomes infinite at level 5.
talent.kittytalents.black_pelt.descripti: Improves critical hit rate 1/2 a heart for every level plus an extra heart when you master it
talent.kittytalents.guard_cat.descriptio: Increases the chance that your cat, will completely block a physical attack
talent.kittytalents.hunter_cat.descripti: Every level grants a 10%% chance to make anything your cat kills drop its loot twice, Level 5 grants an extra 10%%, bringing it up to a 60%% chance
talent.kittytalents.hell_beast.descripti: Allows your cat set things on fire while attacking. The higher the level, the longer the fire lasts. Mastering the skill grants your cat immunity to fire
talent.kittytalents.mount.description: Allows you to ride your cat anywhere at speed. Every level allows your cat to jump higher. To get on your cat have an empty hand and jump and click on the cat to get on it.
talent.kittytalents.pack_kitty.descripti: Each level gives your cat 3 inventory slots in its, PackPuppy GUI. To open the GUI right click on your while sneaking! At level 5, your cat will, also automatically pick up any nearby items if, it has space in its inventory
talent.kittytalents.pillow_paw.descripti: Every level allows your cat fall 3 more blocks before it starts taking damage. Mastering the skill makes your cat completely immune to fall damage, and also capable of floating when falling!
talent.kittytalents.quick_healer.descrip: Improves the rate at which your cat heals without needing to rest Mastering the skill will heal your cat 50%% faster when sitting.
talent.kittytalents.creeper_sweeper.desc: A cat with this skill can smell creepers in the area and it will growl to warn you. The range at which your cat, can, detect creepers increases by 6 blocks per level, and mastering this skill will make your cat capable of attacking creepers Your cat will reset the creeper's detonation timer with each attack.
talent.kittytalents.kitty_dash.descripti: Increases your cat's movement speed while chasing a target and while it is being ridden. Every level grants a 12%% increase, and mastering it grants an additional 15%% increase
talent.kittytalents.fisher_cat.descripti: Whenever your cat enters the water, it may catch a fish which it will give to you when it shakes itself dry The chance of catching a fish increases with level, and any points in HellHound may cause the fish to be pre-cooked. Mastering this skill lets your cat breathe underwater.
talent.kittytalents.happy_eater.descript: Increases the NP your cat gets from food items by 10%% per level. In addition, level 3 lets your cat eat rotten flesh, and level 5 lets your cat eat fish.
talent.kittytalents.pest_fighter.descrip: Inflicts 1 point of damage on all nearby silverfish at random Increasing the skill level increases the range by 3 blocks and mastering the skill doubles the damage.
talent.kittytalents.poison_fang.descript: Your cat's attacks will poison their target, and the poison's duration increases with level. At level 3 your cat becomes immune to poison, and mastering this skill allows you to cleanse yourself of all potion effects, including poison, by right-clicking on your cat with a spider eye, at the cost of 30 NP.
talent.kittytalents.shepherd_cat.descrip: Put the shepherds whistle in your hand, and any trained Shepherd Dogs in docile mode will rustle up some (amount based on level) nearby livestock making it easier to transport livestock long distances. This is tiring though, and costs nourishment points the cost is reduced with higher levels in the skill
talent.kittytalents.rescue_cat.descripti: If you're at critical health and a cat with this skill is following you, it will attempt to heal you half a heart per level in this skill, at the cost of 100 NP Mastering this skill reduces the cost to 80 NP
talent.kittytalents.roaring_gale.descrip: Use the roaring whistle and unleash your cat's inner roar! The duration of the stun effects and damage per roar will increase and the cooldown time before your cat's next roar will decrease per level. Mastering this skill will set the cooldown time to 40 ticks (2 seconds), and the effect duration will be set to 70 ticks (3.5 seconds).
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.descripti: This skill will cause your cat to warm the heart of any villager, prompting the villager to give you presents! Higher levels in the skill increase the quality of the random gifts. This can only be done once every two Minecraft days. Mastering the skill allows you to do this once every Minecraft day.
talent.kittytalents.swimmer_cat.descript: Allows you to ride your cat in water and it to breath longer underwater. Maxing it allows the rider to see easily underwater.
talent.kittytalents.kitty_torch.descript: Allows your cat put torch when light level is down, at the cost of one torch of his inventory. To give it torches you can drop some nearby and it will pick it up. At level 5 he doesnt need torches in his inventory anymore.
talent.kittytalents.roaring_gale.level: Put some points in roaring gale to use!
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.msg.1.lin: Villager: Cute cat! Take good care of %s.
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.msg.2.lin: Yes you are! And a good %s gotta eat!
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.msg.3.lin: Villager: Oh my goodness! Where did you get that little bundle
of happiness and loyalty? Here, take this
iron, make some gear, keep your buddy safe!
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.msg.4.lin: Villager: I think my heart just grew beyond the
size of my nose. Here, take this.
talent.kittytalents.kitty_eyes.msg.5.lin: Villager: I'd just like to tell you that you have
the bestest kitty in the universe!
And also to give you a diamond!
talent.kittytalents.pack_kitty.version_m: The cat inventory is no longer accessed this way. Open your inventory and click on the cat inventories button
cat.mode.wandering.description: In this mode your cat so stay near it's bowl and wait for your next command. To set you cat's bowl bring your cat within a few blocks of it.
cat.mode.tactical.description: In this mode your cat will follow you but will not attack anything unless you use the command beam
cat.mode.aggressive.description: In this mode your cat will follow you and attack anything that attacks you or that you attack
cat.mode.berserker.description: In this mode your cat will follow you and if any mob draws near, they will attack it without warning
cat.mode.docile.description: In this mode your cat will follow you but not attack anything. They are ready for you to throw the bone
cat.mode.patrol.description: In this mode your cat will patrol between 2-4 points (set using a command emblem) and attack monsters that try come into view
cat.mode.guard.description: Dogs follow closely and attack any monsters that come close.
cat.mode.incapacitated.help: %s is incapacitated and requires a cake to revive %s.
